  "text": "The performance of the proposed model in this scenario is illustrated in Table 5 . The table shows that the correct activity was recognized with an F-measure of 88%. Referring to the previous state-of-the-art study in [CITATION_1] , we found that that the average F-measure of our model outperformed that in Reference [CITATION_2] by 8% and 4% for the position-independent and position-aware HAR, respectively. Table 4 . List of evaluation scenarios often used in the literature.",
